<refsect1 id="description-gstmessage">
    <title>Description</title>

    <para>
        Messages are implemented as a subclass of <link linkend="class-gstminiobject"><classname>gst.MiniObject</classname></link> with a generic 
        <link linkend="class-gststructure"><classname>gst.Structure</classname></link> as the content. 
        This allows for writing custom messages without requiring an API change while allowing a wide range of different types of messages.
    </para>
    <para>
        Messages are posted by objects in the pipeline and are passed to the application using the 
        <link linkend="class-gstbus"><classname>gst.Bus</classname></link>.
    </para>
    <para>
        A <link linkend="class-gstelement"><classname>gst.Element</classname></link> usually posts messages on the bus provided 
        by the parent container using <methodname><link linkend="method-gstelement--post-message">gst.Element.post_message()</link></methodname>
    </para>
</refsect1>

